data.description: Welcome to 2909 Hockenhull Dr in Clovis, NM! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts elegant hardwood floors and a spacious kitchen perfect for gatherings. The cozy family room features a fireplace, adding warmth and character. Equipped with modern conveniences, the home includes essential appliances such as a stove, refrigerator, and garbage disposal, along with handy W/D hookups. The versatile layout offers two living spaces, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment. Enjoy the ambiance of the fireplace complete with tools, and take advantage of the practical features like ceiling fans and mini blinds. The property's exterior complements the interior's appeal with a storage shed, covered patio, and a fenced yard, offering additional space for storage, outdoor activities, and privacy.
